IMAPAccount dario
Host dario.test
Port 993
User postmaster@dario.test
Pass "postmaster"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore dario-remote
Account dario

MaildirStore dario-local
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.local/share/mail/dario.test/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/dario.test/Inbox

Channel dario
Far :dario-remote:
Near :dario-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
